是的，可以使用“提取方法（Extract Method）”设计模式来继续重构代码并使其更易读和维护。

例如，可以将负责加载视图的代码提取到一个名为`renderView()`的独立方法中：

```php
public function add()
{
 if ($this->input->post("departmentName")) {
 $departmentName = $this->input->post("departmentName");
 $departmentBudget = $this->input->post("departmentBudget");
 $this->departments\_m->addDepartment($departmentName, $departmentBudget);
 redirect("/departments");
 }
 $data = [
 'title' => 'Add Department - DB Hotel Management System',
 'page' => 'departments'
 ];
 $departments = $this->departments\_m->get\_departments();
 $this->renderView($data, $departments);
}

private function renderView($data, $departments)
{
 $this->load->view('header', $data);
 $this->load->view('departments/add', ['departments' => $departments]);
 $this->load->view('footer');
}
```

这样，代码就更有组织性和易于理解，因为已经将负责加载视图的逻辑分离到了一个独立的方法中。此外，如果将来需要修改加载视图的方式，只需要在`add()`方法的一个地方进行修改，而不需要在代码中的多个地方进行查找。

是的，可以应用 SOLID 原则来重构代码，并使其更加强大、易于维护和未来扩展。例如，可以应用单一职责原则（Single Responsibility Principle, SRP）将视图加载逻辑分离到一个不同的类中，名为 `ViewRenderer`，而不是在方法 `add()` 中将其与业务逻辑混合在一起：
```
class DepartmentsController
{
    private $viewRenderer;
    public function __construct(ViewRenderer $viewRenderer)
    {
        $this->viewRenderer = $viewRenderer;
    }
    public function add()
    {
        if ($this->input->post("departmentName")) {
            $departmentName = $this->input->post("departmentName");
            $departmentBudget = $this->input->post("departmentBudget");
            $this->departments_m->addDepartment($departmentName, $departmentBudget);
            redirect("/departments");
        }
        $data = [
            'title' => 'Add Department - DB Hotel Management System',
            'page' => 'departments'
        ];
        $departments = $this->departments_m->get_departments();
        $this->viewRenderer->render('header', $data);
        $this->viewRenderer->render('departments/add', ['departments' => $departments]);
        $this->viewRenderer->render('footer');
    }
}
class ViewRenderer
{
    public function render($viewName, $data)
    {
        $this->load->view($viewName, $data);
    }
}
```
这样，视图加载逻辑已经分离到不同的类中，使代码更具有模块化和易于维护的特点。此外，通过在 `DepartmentsController` 构造函数中使用依赖注入将 `ViewRenderer` 实例传递给它，而不是在类中创建它，已经实现了依赖反转原则（Dependency Inversion Principle, DIP）。这使得代码更易于测试和未来扩展。

