以下是如何实现在MongoDB上保存用户数据的`UserService`类的示例：

```
import org.springframework.data.mongodb.core.ReactiveMongoTemplate;
import org.springframework.data.mongodb.core.query.Criteria;
import org.springframework.data.mongodb.core.query.Query;
import org.springframework.data.mongodb.core.query.Update;
import reactor.core.publisher.Flux;
import reactor.core.publisher.Mono;

public class UserService {
   private final ReactiveMongoTemplate mongoTemplate;

   public UserService(ReactiveMongoTemplate mongoTemplate) {
      this.mongoTemplate = mongoTemplate;
   }

   public Flux<User> getAllUsers() {
      return mongoTemplate.findAll(User.class);
   }

   public Mono<User> createUser(User user) {
      return mongoTemplate.save(user);
   }

   public Mono<User> getUser(Long id) {
      Query query = Query.query(Criteria.where("id").is(id));
      return mongoTemplate.findOne(query, User.class);
   }

   public Mono<User> updateUser(Long id, User user) {
      Query query = Query.query(Criteria.where("id").is(id));
      Update update = new Update()
         .set("name", user.getName())
         .set("surname", user.getSurname())
         .set("address", user.getAddress());
      return mongoTemplate.findAndModify(query, update, User.class);
   }

   public Mono<Void> deleteUser(Long id) {
      Query query = Query.query(Criteria.where("id").is(id));
      return mongoTemplate.remove(query, User.class);
   }
}
```

在此示例中，`UserService`类使用`ReactiveMongoTemplate`对象在MongoDB上执行读取、创建、更新和删除操作。

